OL,3,C'He wasn't perfect but he didn't
OL,4,Cdeserve to die'
OL,6,FThe family of a man stabbed to death
OL,7,Fin Rotherham a year ago have urged the
OL,8,Fpublic to help police catch his killer.
OL,10,FPaul Sharp, who was 52, was found with
OL,11,Fserious injuries at a property on
OL,12,FRedscope Crescent on the morning of 25
OL,13,FOctober 2023.
OL,15,FHe diad at the scene.
OL,17,FA 47-year-old man was arrested and
OL,18,Fthen re-arrested on suspicion of
OL,19,Fmurder, but has been released on bail
OL,20,Fpending further enquiries.
