OL,3,C'He wasn't perfect but he didn't
OL,4,Cdeserve to die'
OL,6,FDet Insp David Robertson, of South
OL,7,FYorkshire Police, said: "We suspect
OL,8,Fpeople in this community know more
OL,9,Fthan what is being told to us, and we
OL,10,Fare urging those who may have some
OL,11,Finformation that could help us to come
OL,12,Fforward.
OL,14,F"Paul's family deserve answers and I
OL,15,Fwant to reassure them that we are
OL,16,Fdoing all we can to get to the truth."
